  "description": "Planet of Shades is an action arcade game that features gameplay similar to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/cybernoid-the-fighting-machine\">Cybernoid</a>. The player controls an egg-like spaceship and has to find and destroy enemy bases in a big labyrinth. He can control move to up, left and right. The spaceship is falling down on its own. When he moves up, he loses power that has to be replenished in the course of game. His task is not really easy as the labyrinth is full of enemies. Bases can be destroyed with bombs than can be found in multiple places of the labyrinth.<br><br><a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/developer/sheet/view/developerId,548973/\">Miroslav Fídler</a> released  much more popular sequel two years after Planet of Shades. That game is called <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/jet-story\">Jet-Story</a>.",
